npx create-react-app my-app
cd my-app
npm start
Use ES7 React snippets in vscode and use that to automatically give class by typing rce+tab. rconst for constructor
rfce+tab ==> Functional Component
rpce+tab ==> Pure Component
rconst ==> constructor 
rpe ==> memo component

Conventions or Rules to follow 
The function name or class name should always be camelcase, inorder to import it in any other file.
